        "title": "refactor: internalize OpenClaw agent runtime",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- internalize the former Pi agent/runtime package surface under OpenClaw-owned `src/agents/**`, `src/agents/runtime/**`, `src/agents/sessions/**`, and `src/llm/**` modules\n- remove root dependencies on the old Pi agent/AI/coding-agent packages; keep `@earendil-works/pi-tui` only for the existing TUI/session renderer carveout\n- move legacy Pi names to explicit deprecated SDK/doctor compatibility boundaries, with internal callers migrated to OpenClaw runtime names\n- consolidate model/runtime/session wiring so runtime normalization and persisted-session compatibility live in shared OpenClaw helpers instead of scattered legacy branches\n\n## Verification\n\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/agents/embedded-agent-runner/aliases.test.ts src/agents/harness-runtimes.test.ts src/agents/harness/selection.test.ts src/agents/harness/runtime-plugin.test.ts src/agents/openai-codex-routing.test.ts src/agents/runtime-plan/auth.test.ts src/auto-reply/reply/agent-runner-execution.test.ts src/auto-reply/reply/agent-runner-memory.test.ts src/infra/heartbeat-runner.tool-response.test.ts src/commands/doctor/shared/codex-route-warnings.test.ts src/plugins/compat/registry.test.ts src/config/zod-schema.agent-defaults.test.ts src/commands/agent.test.ts` passed, 15 files / 378 tests\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/agents/harness-runtimes.test.ts src/auto-reply/reply/agent-runner-execution.test.ts src/auto-reply/reply/agent-runner-memory.test.ts src/infra/heartbeat-runner.tool-response.test.ts src/plugins/compat/registry.test.ts src/config/zod-schema.agent-defaults.test.ts` passed, 6 files / 186 tests\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/agents/agent-model-discovery.auth.test.ts src/plugins/compat/registry.test.ts src/plugins/runtime/index.test.ts` passed, 4 files / 40 tests\n- `pnpm tsgo:prod` passed\n- `pnpm build` passed; existing rolldown dts warning remains in `src/agents/runtime/harness/messages.d.ts`\n- `git diff --check` passed\n- Codex autoreview after focused fixes: no bugs/regressions found\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\nBehavior addressed: OpenClaw no longer treats the embedded agent runtime as Pi package-owned implementation; Pi-named behavior remains only deprecated plugin compatibility or doctor migration metadata.\n\nReal environment tested: local macOS source checkout on Node/pnpm repo wrappers.\n\nExact steps or command run after this patch: focused Vitest runner commands above, `pnpm tsgo:prod`, `pnpm build`, `git diff --check`, and Codex autoreview.\n\nEvidence after fix: root package/lock/workspace no longer reference old Pi agent/AI/coding-agent packages; targeted scans leave only `@earendil-works/pi-tui` and deprecated SDK/doctor compat markers.\n\nObserved result after fix: tests/typecheck/build all pass on the touched runtime/session/plugin compatibility surfaces.\n\nWhat was not tested: full CI / broad Testbox gate was not run before opening this cleanup PR.\n",
